    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Life on Earth is gone. Death and Decay rules under the surface.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035960/extras/697ad46a9c8abe4e67473b32a4e97911.poster.avif?t=1772371104\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035960/extras/697ad46a9c8abe4e67473b32a4e97911.webm?t=1772371104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035960/extras/697ad46a9c8abe4e67473b32a4e97911.mp4?t=1772371104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Last Chance of Salvation is the Anthem.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035960/extras/510095bb972e1775a18b8d712216ef32.poster.avif?t=1772371104\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035960/extras/510095bb972e1775a18b8d712216ef32.webm?t=1772371104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035960/extras/510095bb972e1775a18b8d712216ef32.mp4?t=1772371104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It says a Warrior will emerge, the first of its kind - The last iteration of Artificial Life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035960/extras/8444de22cf19fd39c433c358246cadfc.poster.avif?t=1772371104\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035960/extras/8444de22cf19fd39c433c358246cadfc.webm?t=1772371104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035960/extras/8444de22cf19fd39c433c358246cadfc.mp4?t=1772371104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Harvest the power of your Augments. Collect and choose your active abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035960/extras/1615e8ca6b9704adfd894baf487f7aac.poster.avif?t=1772371104\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035960/extras/1615e8ca6b9704adfd894baf487f7aac.webm?t=1772371104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035960/extras/1615e8ca6b9704adfd894baf487f7aac.mp4?t=1772371104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the town of Haven and interact with its denizens as you gain new ways to upgrade and build onto your newfound home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035960/extras/68bace6dea5625161d9ba085ccae8590.poster.avif?t=1772371104\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035960/extras/68bace6dea5625161d9ba085ccae8590.webm?t=1772371104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035960/extras/68bace6dea5625161d9ba085ccae8590.mp4?t=1772371104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become the Hero of humanity as you discover the true meaning of the ancient and mysterious Anthem!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035960/extras/d56dfe51f59bcb7ac2a05c7504a04ecc.poster.avif?t=1772371104\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035960/extras/d56dfe51f59bcb7ac2a05c7504a04ecc.webm?t=1772371104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035960/extras/d56dfe51f59bcb7ac2a05c7504a04ecc.mp4?t=1772371104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
